## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources, which may not cover all possible perspectives or the latest research on the topic. Additionally, the subjective nature of customer interactions means that individual experiences can vary widely, and the insights provided may not apply universally. Further research, including empirical studies, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the factors influencing customer interactions.